cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS

This paper is about developing data sets for natural language processing research, specifically for Arabic treebank corpora. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also discusses techniques and models, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of data sets and divisions could also be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
